Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:50.09,0:48:57.00,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたが今も息をしている{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:57.77,0:49:06.78,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけでもう胸はいっぱい{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:07.40,0:49:15.11,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,心の震えあらわす言葉は{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:15.24,0:49:23.22,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うまく探せないけど{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:23.78,0:49:30.56,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたのほほえみ きれいな旋律{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:30.64,0:49:40.01,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,春の野原いちめんに開く小花{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:40.48,0:49:48.08,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やわらかな日ざし 恵の雨粒が{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:48.47,0:49:54.34,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,降りそそぎますように{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:54.81,0:50:00.15,ed_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,天を見上げた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:50.09,0:48:57.00,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你如今仍在轻轻呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:57.77,0:49:06.78,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这样就能填满我心{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:07.40,0:49:15.11,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然而心中悸动{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:15.24,0:49:23.22,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,却难以言表{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:23.78,0:49:30.56,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的微笑是那绮丽的旋律{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:30.64,0:49:40.01,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛春天原野上遍开的小花{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:40.48,0:49:48.08,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,温暖的阳光 恩惠的雨点{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:48.47,0:49:54.34,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,祈祷着它们快些降临{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:54.81,0:50:00.15,ed_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,抬头望向天空{\fad(200,200)}
