Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【Dialogue】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.09,0:00:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才您说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.16,0:00:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的举动总是出人意料让我放心不下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.35,0:00:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是之前的那句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的那句?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.38,0:00:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.14,0:00:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不必太紧张 但千万不能大意哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.04,0:00:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往前一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.30,0:00:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往前?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.16,0:00:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就是修学旅行了吧…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.08,0:00:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.66,0:00:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句又太前了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人该不是在装傻吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.78,0:00:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问了句「带什么礼物回来比较好?」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.83,0:00:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后姐姐大人说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.40,0:00:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你们平安回来就是最好的礼物」这么说的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 您是这么回答的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.32,0:00:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我说「那就不知道买些什么好了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.60,0:00:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人先说了句「如果非得要说什么东西的话」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.42,0:00:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…您没这么说吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.62,0:00:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「罗马馒头 或者是佛罗伦萨煎饼」这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.11,0:01:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在说笑话吧…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.38,0:01:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年我们没买到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有机会的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.20,0:01:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随意买哪怕其中一样带回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.72,0:01:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西在哪里有卖的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.13,0:01:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没买到怎么会知道呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.27,0:01:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是在开玩笑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（他爹真是的…）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.77,0:01:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修学旅行而已却开起送行会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小题大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.31,0:01:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人们呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.00,0:01:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈和阿姨在柜台结帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸在照顾叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.10,0:02:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说大概坐不了电车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我出来叫计程车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醉倒了啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.46,0:02:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醉倒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.68,0:02:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太高兴了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.29,0:02:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃也能自己一个人去修学旅行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.97,0:02:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们年轻人就坐电车回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.04,0:02:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.55,0:02:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去说一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.92,0:02:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.42,0:02:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.54,0:02:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯? 怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.45,0:02:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们早点回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提出一起坐电车回去的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是年轻人什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是想要两人独处的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我才不会跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.69,0:03:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不~ 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.07,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想看到小令一脸臭美的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.95,0:03:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我就稍微当一下温顺的由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这一周里留给小令回忆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有由乃闹着别扭的脸的话就太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 这么晚打电话过来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.77,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有很多人会来做客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家都很晚休息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是志摩子同学你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.83,0:03:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是早睡早起的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.74,0:03:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才在重新检查一遍明天要带的行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 毕竟目的地这么远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说要回来拿就能回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.82,0:03:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是那边有卖的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不敢保证自己能轻松购物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.10,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是忘了东西就会很在意的类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.40,0:04:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些话在学校忘了说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后烦恼了一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.13,0:04:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是决定打电话过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.92,0:04:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路顺风…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万事请多加小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…志摩子同学的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.81,0:04:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不怎么担心会发生什么离谱的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.19,0:04:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.38,0:04:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等着…等着您回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃梨子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.24,0:04:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在本以为是可以随时离开的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.50,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却认识了会守候自己归来的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是靠脚镣禁锢着的鸟笼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.68,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是重要的巢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里 有重要的雏鸟在为我而等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.57,0:05:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿越高大的校门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.94,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让裙子上的褶痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.41,0:05:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让白色的水手领翻起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.61,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒缓地行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.97,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fs35}{\pos(260,518)}成田国际机场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（好高啊~）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（真厉害呢~）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（好紧张~）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像是那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位一起来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 坐机场直达车来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.06,0:07:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 有那种车吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 虽然很花时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.48,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为姐姐大人说拿着这么多行李到处转车太麻烦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打搅了 三位请看这边~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.56,0:07:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算把出发前的白蔷薇大人 红蔷薇花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和黄蔷薇花蕾的样子都拍下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茑子同学 是真美同学拜托你的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美同学即使在校外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也忙进忙出很积极呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.13,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才开始就看见你好几次经过这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.66,0:08:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上我是收到了假情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我跑了好几次服务台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.86,0:08:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假情报?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到广播在找佐藤圣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.52,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤圣!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了是假情报嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.95,0:08:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄错人了…或者应该说是听错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.83,0:08:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被叫的人是姓加东吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.83,0:08:27.09,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}注:日语中加东（カトウ katou）和佐藤（サトウ satou）读音近似
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.59,0:08:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说志摩子同学也听到广播了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.33,0:08:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 虽然一瞬间还以为是叫佐藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫第二遍的时候仔细一听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.10,0:08:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来叫的是加东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使真的是叫佐藤圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.51,0:08:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是同名同姓的可能更大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美同学 真是辛苦您了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得就我一个人慌慌张张的像个傻瓜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.62,0:08:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 藤组和松组是同一路线呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.56,0:08:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 要是相反路线的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.97,0:08:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们松组和志摩子同学就几乎是各走各的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.06,0:09:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢抽到好签的老师和圣母玛莉亚~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.55,0:09:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茑子同学什么时候变成新闻部专属摄影师了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.56,0:09:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 虽然也算是被真美同学拜托的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更主要的是出于我个人的意愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.09,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用相框装饰起来放在学园祭的摄影部展出之类的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学的问题真是一针见血呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能稍微放点水吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等 别这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 茄子~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该是时候到松组那边集合了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已经到集合的时间了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么志摩子同学 回头见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.77,0:09:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是该祝你武运昌隆呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs34}（这次不得不好好控制买特产的数量了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.74,0:09:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs34}（真让人跃跃欲试呢）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.73,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs34}（看来在飞机上要做一下这方面的采访了）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs34}（真是一刻都不得闲啊…）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.93,0:09:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那祐巳同学 祝你旅途愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不时还会碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也祝志摩子同学旅途愉快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茑子同学 你真的不用坐靠窗的位置吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.38,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为比起飞机外面 我对里面更感兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.70,0:10:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 她在颤抖着祈祷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.43,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜有安全带绑着 要不就能到面前去拍下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对人家很失礼的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.34,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…这真是正经而明智的意见呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然确实有点冒犯人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得会是很好的一张照片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同颤抖着的鸟儿般生动的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是太遗憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论对我还是对她来说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好高!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 茑子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母玛莉亚也是像这样注视着我们的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.31,0:11:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收回前言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.63,0:11:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学果然很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.96,0:11:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么刚起床又要睡觉了啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.92,0:11:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘客们处于睡眠状态最有利于机内安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.01,0:11:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以理解为什么祥子大人会一直在睡觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但恐怕结束机内生活时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该觉得自己变成肉用小肥鸡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.25,0:12:06.22,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(185,558)\fad(300,0)}罗马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小时后换搭前往酒店的巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前自由活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但绝对不能离开机场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.89,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}注:罗马费米齐诺机场（Fiumicino Airport） 原名为达·芬奇机场 小说里最初到达的是米兰马尔彭萨\N国际机场（Milan Malpensa International Airport） 购物后才飞往罗马费米齐诺机场 动画中省略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.87,0:12:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要硬币的同学可以提出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来统一兑换
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学你准备怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.92,0:12:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小令把去年没花完带回家的零钱当饯别礼物送给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去换成零钱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.26,0:12:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事情都是一种经验嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 挑战自我~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个应该可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 要上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.60,0:12:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Buon…Buongiorno
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Buonasera
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.73,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}注:这两句是意大利语的问候语 虽然字面直译Buongiorno相当于日语的こんにちは（白天问好用语）\NBuonasera相当于日语的こんばんは（晚安） 实际上意大利人在午休后的问候语就由Buongiorno\N转为Buonasera了 因此常有外国人在下午误用Buongiorno 另外如果是对较熟悉的人就直接说Ciao
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学 由乃同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事情得和你们商量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带回蔷薇馆的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.50,0:13:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用我们三人的名义凑钱买行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.73,0:13:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.33,0:13:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.38,0:13:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回程时在机场买吧 免得带着不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是买吃的比较好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.00,0:13:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近瞳子和可南子也常来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她们的份也加上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.02,0:13:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 早知道就到祐巳同学刚才去的店里先找找看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.61,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但不要紧 回去时也会有时间的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.74,0:13:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于礼物的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.76,0:13:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好建议吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.32,0:13:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 最好是罗马馒头或者是佛罗伦萨煎饼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.54,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22\fad(200,200)}注:卡拉瓦乔饭店（HOTEL SFORZA） 距离机场三公里 三星级 建于1892年 20世纪后期由小旅馆转型为宾馆\N客房均有独立盥洗室 电话 办公桌以及宽带 餐厅提供丹麦 法国 东亚及其它各国的特色菜肴 可容纳170人的\N大礼堂是举办会议的理想场所 中礼堂可容纳50人 还有2间供10-35人使用的小礼堂 标准双人间为120欧元/晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,231号房间…是这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~ 累死我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.70,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 祐巳同学 你喜欢睡这边吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是喜欢的话我就换一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 两边都一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服会变皱的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.48,0:14:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…再稍微过一会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.14,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学 过来泡澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学…你先用吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.83,0:14:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等一会再来…让我睡一会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.85,0:14:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不行了 那就我先洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 对了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.74,0:14:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯? 没有洗身子的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说没法先洗好身体再泡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.87,0:15:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在浴缸里洗头洗脸和洗身体的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.59,0:15:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用过的热水就不得不换掉了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.52,0:15:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行! 在这里睡着的话 淹死了可不是开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学 我已经洗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.92,0:15:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你不洗了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.34,0:15:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要去把热水关掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…不洗了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会再去洗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.76,0:15:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之这样躺着会着凉的 好好睡下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 把制服脱下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.97,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说挂在浴室里能消去皱褶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.59,0:15:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我起不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 起来喽~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯? 由乃同学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.80,0:16:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你发烧了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.45,0:16:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不觉得祐巳的手凉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可能不怎么严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很严重了啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.86,0:16:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我刚洗完澡全身都很热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.68,0:16:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫老师来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.93,0:16:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的…拜托…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻微发烧而已 是老毛病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.22,0:16:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用湿毛巾冷敷在额头上躺着休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.56,0:16:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过段时间就会好的 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.06,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是老毛病了对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.18,0:16:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷敷一下额头就能好了是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.78,0:16:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这么办吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.98,0:17:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾用旅馆里最小的那种行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.34,0:17:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…请你用我放在拉杆包口袋里的小毛巾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.86,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉杆包口袋里是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.54,0:17:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个看上去用了好久了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是有魔法的毛巾哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都帮我退烧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.50,0:17:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候要是没有它就睡不着觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.49,0:17:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗? 那就再让它派上用场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢 舒服多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗? 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心脏的毛病虽然不再复发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是疲劳的话 有时还是会发烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.06,0:17:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 发烧的次数已经渐渐减少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 要是让老师知道的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.91,0:18:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕又不能和大家一起行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.90,0:18:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.69,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.33,0:18:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说所谓朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.93,0:18:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了吃亏才存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要太在意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.86,0:18:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 蓉子大人她曾这么说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.83,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是淋浴的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 由乃同学!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.87,0:18:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在厕所? 哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.95,0:18:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是倒在里面了吧?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…快去找老师来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哼歌?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要上厕所?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.00,0:19:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗? 那不好意思了 让我先把头发弄干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白担心一场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~ 舒爽多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.63,0:19:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.04,0:19:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老毛病了 说过冷敷着额头睡觉就能好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说归说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.53,0:19:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的制服 我洗澡前已经从浴室拿出来放到壁橱里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.41,0:19:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没沾上湿气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.77,0:20:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你担心了吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.29,0:20:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到我脆弱一面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同年级里可只有祐巳同学一个而已哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被灌了这样一句迷魂汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只好就这样随她去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可真是让我担心了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.94,0:20:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在分房间时由乃她强烈要求和我分在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.60,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就是担心会不会发生昨天那样的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.47,0:20:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得排多久的队啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…大概还要一小时左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家太散漫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.09,0:20:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散漫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是在批评啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.39,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫不经心可以是因为豁达大方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以说是宽容吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是说和日本不同而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.17,0:21:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说谁好谁坏 而是说一个国家的特征吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能发现更多的新鲜之处就好了
