Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.77,0:29:46.07,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(500,518)\fad(300,300)}《受胎告知》（安哲理柯）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.77,0:29:46.07,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22\fad(200,200)}《受胎告知》:耶稣降生的第一个故事 描绘有一对双翼的天使来朝拜年轻的圣母玛莉亚 告诉她怀孕了 救苦救难的\N基督将要出生 意大利文艺复兴初期的壁画家弗拉·安哲理柯（Fra Angelico）所作 收藏于圣马可修道院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.31,0:30:00.00,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(167,563)\fad(500,0)}比萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.43,0:30:02.93,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(240,518)\fad(300,300)}奇迹广场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.43,0:30:02.93,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26\fad(300,300)}奇迹广场（Campo dei Miracoli）:在比萨城的北面 广场中间是大片的草坪 散布着一组宗教建筑\N每座建筑相对独立 由大圣堂（Duomo）洗礼堂（Battistero）肯波山托大公墓（Camposanto）\N和斜塔（Torre Pendente）（大圣堂附属钟楼）组成  广场周围还保留着古代的城墙和城门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:08.09,0:30:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是斜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.42,0:30:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得重心倾斜了好不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.18,0:30:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过令大人竟然允许你攀登斜塔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:38.44,0:30:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有去申请小令的许可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:41.43,0:30:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是她自己误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.43,0:30:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「祐巳她们要去攀登斜塔呢 真有胆量啊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.93,0:30:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是这么一说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.70,0:30:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学…你居然会没被真理之口咬到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.70,0:30:53.66,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}注:真理之口（Bocca della verita）嵌于柯斯梅汀圣母教堂门廊上的一块有着狰狞脸谱的大理石板上\N据说可能是古时的排水口盖 石板上的脸谱是海神与人鱼所生的儿子 (希腊神特理顿)  中世纪时人们\N认为石板上的大嘴代表了神的判决 传说说谎者将手伸进真理之口 口里的獠牙就会咬掉说谎者的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.46,0:30:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没撒谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:06.45,0:31:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.68,0:31:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还能往上爬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:09.77,0:31:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.92,0:31:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:12.10,0:31:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.92,0:31:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:16.15,0:31:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我还担心你们三个说还想爬呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.63,0:31:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茑子同学竟然是这种事情无法主动开口的类型?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.68,0:31:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.85,0:31:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:34.61,0:31:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.82,0:31:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑蔷薇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.39,0:31:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静大人…你怎么…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.57,0:31:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是来见你们几位的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:45.65,0:31:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我们的行程表的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:48.97,0:31:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有笔友向我泄露情报了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.76,0:31:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笔友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.21,0:31:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.66,0:31:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.43,0:32:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是志摩子哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.85,0:32:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:02.10,0:32:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两位是…笔友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:04.73,0:32:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么奇怪的地方吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.08,0:32:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.11,0:32:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能稍微打扰一下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.93,0:32:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是新闻部的山口真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.56,0:32:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻说圣大人来到了意大利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.07,0:32:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静大人你收到什么消息了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.90,0:32:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.04,0:32:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.33,0:32:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没听说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.35,0:32:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是来了怎么也不和我联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:26.97,0:32:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把我的住址和电话号码都给她了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:30.59,0:32:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那果然是假情报啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:33.29,0:32:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们四人都去攀登斜塔了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.56,0:32:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.36,0:32:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.88,0:32:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有空的话跟我一起去洗礼堂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.88,0:32:40.98,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}洗礼堂（Battistero di San Giovanni）:比萨大圣堂广场上有比萨斜塔 大圣堂 洗礼堂等等建筑 其中洗礼堂是\N位于大圣堂西侧的圆筒形建筑物 直径约35米 于1152年完工 工程费时200余年 通体覆盖白色大理石 建筑物\N下部为罗马式建筑风格 装饰着与大圣堂一样的列柱和拱门 但上部则装饰着哥特式的尖塔群 因此十分罕见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.64,0:32:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很喜欢那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.83,0:32:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.86,0:32:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 像个很大的浴池呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:00.90,0:33:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以喜欢这里 正因为这里像个大浴场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.97,0:34:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么曲子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:25.93,0:34:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即兴之作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.04,0:34:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现成的曲子里想不到刚好能和回音协调成和声的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:31.28,0:34:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想试一次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.49,0:34:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好借你们的东风要了次发挥的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:36.82,0:34:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学 我们去一下洗手间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:44.33,0:34:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也回藤组去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:47.47,0:34:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗? 谢谢你陪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.19,0:34:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该是我说谢谢才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:53.69,0:34:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会写信给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:56.03,0:34:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要写哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.55,0:34:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:04.84,0:35:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静大人住在这附近吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.20,0:35:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是这么近呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:11.29,0:35:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我寄宿在跟意大利人结婚的叔母家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.35,0:35:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在亲戚家 你的父母也很安心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:21.41,0:35:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话多到我都烦不胜烦了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.39,0:35:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是听到他们说 没变化吧 还好吗 想听听你的声音时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:29.99,0:35:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是很高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.25,0:35:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们很在乎我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:34.48,0:35:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很坦白 所以很好懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.08,0:35:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静大人不会打电话回去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.01,0:35:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为国际长途太贵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.95,0:35:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要是用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.38,0:35:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为父母都不会电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.78,0:35:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就寄不了电子邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.98,0:35:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以来到这种观光地的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.62,0:36:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会买当地的美术明信片寄回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:00.85,0:36:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是邮件 也得寄航空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.50,0:36:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那张美术明信片是在哪买的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:07.68,0:36:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在特产店? 邮票呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.66,0:36:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能失陪去买一下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.70,0:36:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了? 冷静一点 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:15.80,0:36:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.56,0:36:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先坐在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:23.78,0:36:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想寄明信片到日本?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:27.12,0:36:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:29.33,0:36:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是给祥子同学吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:31.48,0:36:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.37,0:36:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 送给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.26,0:36:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有邮票哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:40.53,0:36:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:41.50,0:36:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…请把这个卖给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:43.77,0:36:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.57,0:36:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 这种时候只需说声谢谢就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:50.16,0:36:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:52.88,0:36:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想装装长辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:55.04,0:36:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 我就收下你的邮票钱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.06,0:36:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:03.93,0:37:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 静大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:05.70,0:37:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:06.79,0:37:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安用意大利语应该怎么说?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.31,0:37:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.80,0:37:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你好的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.98,0:37:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就是Buongiorno
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.18,0:37:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是给祥子同学的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:17.78,0:37:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需Ciao就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:19.81,0:37:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ciao?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.01,0:37:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 如果要说 贵安 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.12,0:37:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是Ciao Sorella了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.71,0:37:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 还没认妹妹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:34.04,0:37:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:35.53,0:37:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学不会对你唠叨吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.51,0:37:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在暂时没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:39.24,0:37:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:40.68,0:37:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不久之后 你就不能再这么自在了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.96,0:37:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要趁现在好好撒娇才对哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.09,0:37:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（现在我在比萨 旅行非常快乐 祐巳）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:59.71,0:38:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（姐姐大人）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.11,0:38:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我想见你）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:27.53,0:38:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.95,0:38:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学 那个厕所居然是收费的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.21,0:38:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要付钱给入口的大婶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.85,0:38:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她还会找钱算是有良心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.75,0:38:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那个厕所也漂亮得值得付钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:41.82,0:38:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回来的路上我们三个商量了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.61,0:38:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不想去吃意大利冰淇淋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.61,0:38:47.71,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs21}Gelato:意大利语 意即「新鲜的冰淇淋」 其特点 一是新鲜 配方中无任何色素和防腐剂 用新鲜牛奶为基底料搭配浓厚的\N各式调味原料 如果汁 果肉 葡萄糖及少量可可粉或香草等直接搅拌冷冻而成 没有多余的水和空气在里面 所以份量厚实\N而不会觉得坚硬 入口香滑绵密 如丝绸一般柔顺浓郁 二是低热量 配方中绝不以添加奶油的手法来增加口感与浓稠度\N每100克冰淇淋只含有110-140卡的热量 比起Ice Cream少了许多热量和脂肪 新鲜健康低脂低糖 吃了没有肥胖的负担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.19,0:38:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说我们攀登斜塔的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.64,0:38:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逸绘同学她们去吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.27,0:38:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西班牙广场的台阶那里没吃到呢 是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.28,0:38:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意大利冰淇淋店的话 这附近就有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.67,0:39:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静大人也一起来怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:02.23,0:39:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家都说过话了 我也差不多该告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.49,0:39:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得回家预习一下明天的功课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:10.28,0:39:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了祐巳 我帮你把明信片也一起寄了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:15.00,0:39:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很多地方都有邮筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.25,0:39:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但真找起来却不太容易发现呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.79,0:39:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:28.33,0:39:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢您 帮大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:33.58,0:39:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 再会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:35.59,0:39:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认了妹妹的话 记得写信汇报哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:39.39,0:39:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.21,0:39:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.18,0:39:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被摆了一道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.40,0:39:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收下喽~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.15,0:39:53.92,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(266,564)\fad(300,300)}佛罗伦萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.15,0:39:53.92,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(333,468)\fad(300,300)}佛罗伦萨碧提宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.80,0:39:57.30,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,518)\fad(300,300)}佛罗伦萨韦奇奥宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.65,0:40:01.15,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(290,518)\fad(300,300)}佛罗伦萨旧桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.85,0:40:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给瞳子和可南子她们买什么礼物好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.72,0:40:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买东西给她们好是好 不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.56,0:40:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:16.73,0:40:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学 到底认哪个做妹妹啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:20.36,0:40:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为两人一块认是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.19,0:40:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别让她们太过期待了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.02,0:40:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待吗…那由乃你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:29.42,0:40:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在梵蒂冈给未来的妹妹选好念珠了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.45,0:40:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不买了 我改变主意了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:36.52,0:40:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法想像对方的样子而要挑选礼物太空虚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:41.62,0:40:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.87,0:40:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:44.05,0:40:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我应该找个就算把小令给的重要念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.56,0:40:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转送给她都不觉得可惜的可爱妹妹才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:59.27,0:41:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:02.24,0:41:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:03.77,0:41:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛罗伦萨好地方 值得一游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:06.64,0:41:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在说日语…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.43,0:41:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛罗伦萨煎饼 佛罗伦萨煎饼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.45,0:41:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手啦 佐藤同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.45,0:41:16.38,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}注:从鹦鹉说的话中可以推测出圣大人并非单独旅行 根据之前机场里的人名误会猜测\N这位神秘的旅伴很可能是TV第2季12话「青い傘」中登场的圣的大学同学 加东景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:19.23,0:41:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤同学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.61,0:41:29.62,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(236,564)\fad(400,400)}威尼斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.61,0:41:29.62,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(403,468)\fad(400,400)}威尼斯圣马可大教堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.88,0:41:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你觉不觉得那是在说圣大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:39.38,0:41:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.86,0:41:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 就算想破脑袋也不可能有结论的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:44.57,0:41:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非圣大人现在马上出现在我们面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:49.48,0:41:51.98,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,518)\fad(300,300)}威尼斯叹息桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:49.48,0:41:51.98,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs21\fad(200,200)}叹息桥（Ponte dei Sospiri）:建于1603年的早期巴洛克式建筑 两端连结着总督府和威尼斯监狱 是古代由法院向监狱押送\N死囚的必经之路 因犯人过此往往感叹这吸进的最后一口新鲜空气而叹息不已而得名 另外还有一个有趣的传说 一名死囚\N看见从前的恋人在桥彼端与新欢亲热而不禁深深叹息 从此成为了恋人见证爱情的地方 据说在桥下接吻就可以天长地久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:56.84,0:41:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说在通过这座桥底的时候接吻的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.71,0:42:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能得到永远的真爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:03.40,0:42:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而实际上是因为以前的囚犯在穿过这座桥之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:06.18,0:42:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惋惜此身不再有回归之日而叹气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:09.81,0:42:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此而得名叹息桥的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.58,0:42:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你别破坏我们的美梦啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.18,0:42:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 就算是因囚犯的叹息而得名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:21.36,0:42:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不至于就否定亲吻的传说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:25.24,0:42:27.74,ad,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(370,518)\fad(300,300)}威尼斯圣马可广场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.45,0:42:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有在佛罗伦萨的市街上找到煎饼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:39.50,0:42:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同组的人也说没听说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.28,0:42:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西怎么可能有得卖嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.30,0:42:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:48.24,0:42:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送巧克力应该就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.98,0:42:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这就跟去年一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:53.81,0:42:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不够特别 不过还是很好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:58.68,0:43:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.23,0:43:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于圣大人的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.91,0:43:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.29,0:43:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到她了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:09.97,0:43:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但我能感觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.60,0:43:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉到她就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:14.98,0:43:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…为什么圣大人不来见我们呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.05,0:43:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说也许有点自作多情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.92,0:43:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她是在为我着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.85,0:43:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.93,0:43:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想对姐姐大人说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:38.80,0:43:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ciao Sorella
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:40.89,0:43:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想快点见到姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:02.73,0:44:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:04.84,0:44:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:07.27,0:44:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照了很多相片吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.03,0:44:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 茑子同学帮我们照了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.73,0:44:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗? 玩得开心吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:14.56,0:44:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:16.08,0:44:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.60,0:44:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…可是还是没找到罗马馒头和佛罗伦萨煎饼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.08,0:44:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:24.52,0:44:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦? 你当真了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.69,0:44:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然是跟你开玩笑嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:28.88,0:44:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩笑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:30.50,0:44:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:31.26,0:44:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳不也是知道是笑话 那时候才笑了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:36.00,0:44:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是在笑…倒不如说是僵笑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:40.13,0:44:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪呢 那可是圣大人开过的玩笑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:43.55,0:44:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来对祐巳行不通呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:45.76,0:44:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:48.72,0:44:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给您的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:50.45,0:44:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.42,0:44:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也买礼物给一年级生她们了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:55.62,0:44:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 乃梨子的是志摩子同学给她买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:59.20,0:45:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就买了瞳子和可南子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:18.29,0:45:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然由乃同学忠告过会让她们过份期待所以最好别买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:23.87,0:45:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可还是不由自主…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:26.28,0:45:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕让她们有所期待吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:28.32,0:45:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园祭还要麻烦她们多帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:30.78,0:45:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我还给花寺的各位也买了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:35.55,0:45:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:36.86,0:45:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是抱着得到帮助的感谢之心是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.57,0:45:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:41.23,0:45:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能会被说是八面玲珑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:44.55,0:45:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:46.81,0:45:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你的心意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:50.93,0:45:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去请茑子加印几张吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:55.23,0:45:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加印什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:57.64,0:45:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:05.96,0:46:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺好吃吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.56,0:46:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.92,0:46:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（你进步了呢）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:10.27,0:46:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（真的? 妈妈还要我下次把爸爸的便当也一起做了呢）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:15.14,0:46:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（那很好啊 叔父也一定很高兴的）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:17.89,0:46:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（那要是爸爸觉得好 我就给小令做吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:05.95,0:46:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}【那个 志摩子同学】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.43,0:46:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}【怎么了? 乃梨子】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.97,0:46:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}【给家里带的礼物是什么?】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:12.59,0:46:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}【你猜是什么?】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.03,0:46:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}【嗯…什么呢…吃的吗?】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.15,0:46:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}【嗯 猜对了】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:18.92,0:46:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}【吃的吗…是意大利面!】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:17.22,0:46:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:20.70,0:46:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:29.43,0:46:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:31.00,0:46:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀 为什么要做这种没前没后的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:36.10,0:46:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没前没后?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:37.83,0:46:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是往体育馆的舞台搬东西时前后不对了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:42.04,0:46:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说给各个社团部长发通知时的顺序搞错了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:47.63,0:46:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:49.08,0:46:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在山百合会的工作做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:52.35,0:46:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我很认可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:54.90,0:46:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:58.95,0:47:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不经过大脑就做了的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:01.97,0:47:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在却要我承担不良后果 你该怎么补偿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:06.22,0:47:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你还居然做过就算 都忘得一干二净了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:10.90,0:47:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:12.12,0:47:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.92,0:47:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:17.75,0:47:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才寄到 让我怎么回应才好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.11,0:47:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明每天都在见面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:24.50,0:47:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:25.74,0:47:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静大人明明说过航空邮件很花时间…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:30.07,0:47:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那是什么时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:32.20,0:47:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天回家的时候送来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:34.58,0:47:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:36.50,0:47:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…好难堪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:40.50,0:47:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:42.45,0:47:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这封信就当没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:44.96,0:47:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当作没有寄过?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:46.56,0:47:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:48.62,0:47:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这当然要放在祐巳送的相册里面和祐巳的相片一起珍藏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:57.60,0:47:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一辈子都不会忘记的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:03.46,0:48:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 就是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:10.36,0:48:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来想见面的…不只是我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:21.46,0:48:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一辈子都不会忘记…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:24.41,0:48:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.35,0:48:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.02,0:48:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人原来是带着有点恼羞成怒的心情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:21.57,0:50:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(563,360)\fad(500,500)}第四季     制作决定
